query:
SELECT id, direction, entryPrice, exitPrice, pnl, status, entryTime, exitTime, contractId 
FROM positions 
WHERE DATE(entryTime) = DATE('now') 
AND status = 'CLOSED'
ORDER BY entryTime DESC 
LIMIT 10;
